---
title: Za'atar Crusted Halloumi with Israeli Couscous Salad and Yogurt Dressing
description: Coating delicious halloumi slices in za'atar, is changing the game of quick and simple summer salads! Spinach is topped with pearl couscous that has been tossed in a DIY yogurt dressing. Each bite of this salad is unique and satisfying!
